{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775899875528,"sessionID":"ses_28423e195ffe8TXj4LBUSb69pE","part":{"id":"prt_d7be193f2001oqgWJDTZqF4KrI","messageID":"msg_d7be18374001ijaGAC5RO8GmNi","sessionID":"ses_28423e195ffe8TXj4LBUSb69pE","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_fb845e7b55c048939dc7a721","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md","limit":80},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-038: Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager) — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`\n6: - **Language:** Go\n7: - **Size:** L\n8: - **Base specs:** `deployment/client-go.md`\n9: \n10: ## Scope\n11: \n12: This delta spec defines the unit test coverage gaps for the `pkg/workloadmanager` module. Existing tests cover `handler/sandbox_delete_test.go`, `handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go`, `reconciler/metrics_test.go`, and `response/response_test.go`. This spec covers the **untested** code paths.\n13: \n14: ---\n15: \n16: ## R-1: Sandbox 创建 — AgentRuntime\n17: \n18: **Scope:** `handler/sandbox_create.go` — `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox`, `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR`, `rollbackCR`, `generateSessionID`, `generateSandboxName`, `RandString`, `getPortsOrDefaults`, `buildEntryPoints`, `injectPicodAuthEnv`, `resolvePodIP`\n19: \n20: ### Requirement: CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox 成功路径\n21: \n22: #### Scenario: 成功创建 AgentRuntime Sandbox\n23: \n24: - **GIVEN** 有效的 CreateSandboxRequest（Kind=\"AgentRuntime\", Name, Namespace 已填）\n25:   AND DynamicClient 已配置\n26:   AND AgentRuntime CR 模板存在于目标 namespace\n27:   AND Store 可写\n28:   AND Reconciler.WatchSandboxOnce 可正常返回 channel\n29: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox(c *gin.Context)` 被调用\n30: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 201\n31:   AND 响应体包含 SessionID, SandboxID, SandboxName, EntryPoints\n32:   AND AgentRuntime CR 已创建到集群\n33:   AND Sandbox 信息已持久化到 Store\n34:   AND 响应中 EntryPoints 包含从 PodIP + TargetPorts 构建的 endpoint 列表\n35: \n36: ### Requirement: CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox 校验失败\n37: \n38: #### Scenario: 请求体 JSON 解析失败\n39: \n40: - **GIVEN** 请求体为非法 JSON\n41: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 被调用\n42: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 400\n43:   AND 响应包含 JSON 解析错误信息\n44: \n45: #### Scenario: 请求体校验失败 — 缺少必填字段\n46: \n47: - **GIVEN** CreateSandboxRequest 缺少 Name 或 Namespace\n48: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 被调用\n49: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 400\n50:   AND 响应包含校验失败信息\n51:   AND 未创建任何 CR\n52:   AND Store 未被写入\n53: \n54: ### Requirement: CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox 模板不存在\n55: \n56: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime 模板未找到\n57: \n58: - **GIVEN** 有效的 CreateSandboxRequest\n59:   AND 目标 namespace 中不存在匹配的 AgentRuntime CR 模板\n60: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 被调用\n61: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 404\n62:   AND 响应体包含 \"agent runtime template not found\" 类错误\n63:   AND 未创建 Sandbox CR\n64: \n65: ### Requirement: CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox CR 创建失败自动回滚\n66: \n67: #### Scenario: Sandbox CR 创建失败触发回滚\n68: \n69: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 模板存在\n70:   AND 动态客户端在创建 Sandbox CR 时返回错误（如网络不可达）\n71: - **WHEN** `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox` 被调用\n72: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 500\n73:   AND 已创建的 AgentRuntime CR 被 `rollbackCR` 清理\n74:   AND Store 中无残留记录\n75: \n76: ### Requirement: buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR 注入元数据\n77: \n78: #### Scenario: CR 构建包含所有必需 label 和 annotation\n79: \n80: - **GIVEN** AgentRuntime 模板 CR\n\n(Showing lines 1-80 of 826. Use offset=81 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-038: Go 单元测试 (workloadmanager) — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `pkg/workloadmanager`\n- **Language:** Go\n- **Size:** L\n- **Base specs:** `deployment/client-go.md`\n\n## Scope\n\nThis delta spec defines the unit test coverage gaps for the `pkg/workloadmanager` module. Existing tests cover `handler/sandbox_delete_test.go`, `handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go`, `reconciler/metrics_test.go`, and `response/response_test.go`. This spec covers the **untested** code paths.\n\n---\n\n## R-1: Sandbox 创建 — AgentRuntime\n\n**Scope:** `handler/sandbox_create.go` — `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox`, `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR`, `rollbackCR`, `generateSessionID`, `generateSandboxName`, `RandString`, `getPortsOrDefaults`, `buildEntryPoints`, `injectPicodAuthEnv`, `resolvePodIP`\n\n### Requirement: CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox 成功路径","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775899875518,"end":1775899875527}}}}
